      "content": "After simplifying the pressure plate as a cantilever bending member, compare the allowable stress with the computed maximum bending normal stress at the dangerous section m-m. Answer format: allowable_stress>actual_stress or allowable_stress<actual_stress, with no units, explanatory text, or equals signs."
